tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE property_viewings (
    viewing_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    viewer_name VARCHAR(50),
    viewing_date DATE,
    viewing_time TIME
)

CREATE TABLE schedule (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    date DATE,
    start_time TIME,
    end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE Property(
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    address VARCHAR(255),
    city VARCHAR(100),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    zipcode VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE Agent(
    agent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE ViewingSchedule(
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    agent_id INT,
    scheduled_time TIMESTAMP,
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE OpenHouse(
    open_house_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    scheduled_time TIMESTAMP,
    max_guests INT,
    status VARCHAR(20)
);
